snippet.title: Alan Wake (E3 2006 Trailer | HD)
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer of Alan Wake shown on the E3 2006. Alan Wake is a horror action adventure developed by Remedy Entertainment, the creators of the legendary Max Payne franchise.

Note that this trailer still stated that the game was going to be published for both, PC and Xbox 360, while the final game has (so far) only been made available for Xbox.
